<p><div align="center"><table width="50%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Megachile inermis</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Provancher, 1888</font></b><br>
<small><i>Megachile simplex_homonym </i>Provancher, 1882; <i>Megachile inermis </i>Provancher, 1888, replacement name; <i>Megachile simplicissima </i>Dalla Torre, 1896, unnecessary replacement name; <i>Megachile sapellonis </i>Cockerell, 1900; <i>Megachile temporalis </i>Friese, 1903, male not female; <i>Megachile decipiens </i>Lovell and Cockerell, 1907; <i>Cyphopyga inermis </i>&#40;Provancher, 1882&#41;</small><p>
